reviewText: When board anything American Pie always seems to take the edge off.  Somehow teenage years are better when they're on tv.

An excellent value for your money, this package features 4 spin-offs of the 4 original American Pie movies. However, unlike those 4 mainstream American Pie movies, these 4 (band camp/the naked mile/beta house/the book of love) feature tons of nudity/hot girls (WHO DOESN'T LIKE THAT???) and scenes of nasty, shocking, unbelievably gross yet hysterical situations that you'll pee in your pants!
these are such classics! every time we watch them we still laugh as though it was the first time we seen them. lol
the price was perfect to get the whole 4 pack. No complaints. Unrated versions are obviously better. Buying separately would have stunk so it was great to get them all.

While the humor is sometimes slapstick I have really enjoyed all of the American Pie movies.  These four movies were a great addition to the four primary American Pie/ American Wedding/ American Reunion films.

It starts to get redundant fast, but then you knew that when you bought in.  There are some very funny lines/scenes, some very gross humor (no surprises there if you've watched any of these before), and some just stupid waste of film.  Overall, a decent buy if you've followed the series.

All four movies are great. Naked Mile and Beta House are the best. They both contain at least one full frontal and have the most topless women and they are the funniest. Band Camp and Book of Love are also good but not as good as the other two.

American Pie helped revolutionize the modern raunchy comedy. These are side stories focused on the Stifler clan and although very different from their source material are still able to feel like American pie. The movies are nothing special or even fantastic but are still able to be enjoyable for the same audience that once enjoyed the original American pie moveis.
